data.title: Dodge Veterinary Clinic
data.meta_description: Dodge Veterinary Clinic, located in Dodge Center, MN, provides veterinary services for both companion animals and large animals. Contact the clinic today for an appointment!
data.text:
At Dodge Veterinary Clinic, we are committed to providing the highest level of veterinary care to your dogs, cats, goats, sheep, and swine. We believe in client education, compassionate care, and responsible pet ownership.

​

Dodge Veterinary Clinic has been serving the needs of Dodge Center, MN, and the surrounding communities for over 65 years. We provide a variety of companion animal and large animal services, including wellness care and immunizations to whole herd care.

​

We are proud members of the American Veterinary Medical Association (AVMA), Minnesota Veterinary Medical Association (MVMA), and Veterinary Hospitals Association (VHA).
